---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/Main.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for venturarodriguez.xyz, including data handling, user rights, and crypto tool disclosures."
>
  <section class="md:px-16 xs:px-6 px-4 md:pb-16 pb-4 pt-6 md:pt-24">
    <div class="prose mx-auto">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 2026</p>

      <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
      <p>
        In accordance with the applicable data protection regulations,
        particularly the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the
        Spanish Organic Law on Data Protection and Digital Rights (LOPDGDD), the
        data controller of this website is:
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Buenaventura Rodríguez Serrano</strong><br />
        Spain<br />
        Email: ventu.kudu@gmail.com<br />
        Website: https://www.venturarodriguez.xyz
      </p>

      <h2>2. Purpose of Data Processing</h2>
      <p>
        This website provides <strong
          >technical crypto tools for personal use</strong
        >. Personal data collected may be used for:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Responding to inquiries sent through contact methods.</li>
        <li>Maintaining security and functionality of the website.</li>
        <li>Analyzing website usage to improve technical tools.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        <strong>Important:</strong> This is a technical tool, NOT a financial service.
        No investment advice, portfolio management, or financial services are provided.
      </p>
      <p>No automated decision-making or profiling is carried out.</p>

      <h2>3. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
      <p>The legal basis for processing your personal data may include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Your <strong>consent</strong>, when you voluntarily contact the
          website owner.
        </li>
        <li>
          The <strong>legitimate interest</strong> of maintaining the security and
          functionality of the website.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Data Collected</h2>
      <p>This website may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Name (if voluntarily provided)</li>
        <li>Email address (if voluntarily provided)</li>
        <li>Information voluntarily included in messages</li>
        <li>
          Basic technical data (IP address, browser type, access time) for
          security
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Crypto/Blockchain Data:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>We do NOT collect or store wallet addresses</strong></li>
        <li><strong>We do NOT collect or store transaction data</strong></li>
        <li>Blockchain transactions are public/immutable</li>
        <li>Wallet connections are client-side only (via AppKit)</li>
        <li>No KYC/AML data collection</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Information is only collected when voluntarily provided or from standard
        web logs.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        Personal data will only be kept for as long as necessary to fulfill the
        purpose for which it was collected, or to comply with legal obligations.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Data Sharing & Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        Personal data will <strong>not be sold, rented, or shared</strong>,
        except for:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Website hosting services</li>
        <li>Legal obligations</li>
        <li>Technical service providers</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Crypto Tool Integrations:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>0x Protocol</strong> - Swap execution (API)</li>
        <li><strong>Reown AppKit</strong> - Wallet connection (client-side)</li>
        <li><strong>Alchemy</strong> - Blockchain RPC access</li>
        <li><strong>Vercel</strong> - Hosting platform</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        These are technical integrations, NOT financial partnerships. We share
        only necessary technical data for tool functionality.
      </p>
      <p>All providers comply with applicable data protection regulations.</p>

      <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This website may use technical or analytical cookies necessary for the
        functioning and improvement of the website.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can configure your browser to refuse or delete cookies at any time.
      </p>

      <h2>8. User Rights</h2>
      <p>Under the GDPR, users have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access their personal data</li>
        <li>Request rectification of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request erasure of their data</li>
        <li>Request restriction of processing</li>
        <li>Object to processing</li>
        <li>Request data portability</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        To exercise any of these rights, you may contact:
        <strong>ventu.kudu@gmail.com</strong>
      </p>
      <p>
        Users also have the right to lodge a complaint with the Spanish Data
        Protection Authority:
      </p>
      <p>
        Agencia Española de Protección de Datos (AEPD)<br />
        https://www.aepd.es
      </p>

      <h2>9. Crypto Risk & Responsibility</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>This is a technical tool, NOT financial advice.</strong> Cryptocurrency
        investments carry extreme risk. You could lose 100% of your funds.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>We provide NO investment advice</li>
        <li>We have NO custody of your funds</li>
        <li>You control your own wallet</li>
        <li>Blockchain transactions are irreversible</li>
        <li>Prices are extremely volatile</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Use this tool at your own risk. Only risk what you can afford to lose.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Children's Information</h2>
      <p>
        This website is not directed at children under the age of 18 due to
        crypto risks, and the website owner does not knowingly collect personal
        data from children.
      </p>

      <h2>11. EU Crypto Regulations (MiCA)</h2>
      <p>
        This tool operates as a <strong>personal technical utility</strong>, not
        a regulated Crypto Asset Service Provider (CASP).
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>No custody of user assets</li>
        <li>No KYC/AML procedures</li>
        <li>No investment advice or management</li>
        <li>No guaranteed returns or outcomes</li>
        <li>Optional donations only (no mandatory fees)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        If regulatory interpretation changes, this tool may be modified or
        discontinued.
      </p>

      <h2>12. Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Updates will be
        published on this page with the corresponding revision date.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
